\sum_{n > 0} \sum_{m \in \mathbb{Z}} \frac{1}{m^2+n^2t^2}
\sum_{m \in \mathbb{Z}} \frac{1}{m^2+n^2 t^2} = \frac{\pi}{n t} \frac{1+e^{-2 n t}}{1-e^{-2 n t}}
