1/n
n
\frac{\pi}{t} \sum_{n>0} \frac{1}{n}
\sum_{n>0} \sum_{m \in \mathbb{Z}}\frac{1}{m^2+n^2} \ge \sum_{n > 0} \sum_{m=1}^n \frac{1}{m^2+n^2} \ge \sum_{n>0}\sum_{m=1}^n \frac{1}{2n^2}=\sum_{n>0}\frac{1}{2n}
